				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Standing at the entrance of Moonrise Tower, the guard is keeping eye on all the fresh blood seeking audience with the Absolute. The player can influence the guard to send the pilgrims to their death in Town, or to take a chance on them and send them as fodder to colony. Either way the pilgrims will have a bad time."
